    "text": "F1:\t[2023/05/16 16:27:40 GMT+0000] <span id=\"node3_169254084843023138\" class=\"highlighted\">Let's see, okay</span>?<br><br>\t'I took the evidence round to the sheriff hoping it would change his mind, but he didn't care that Nick really was chasing after someone that night.&nbsp; The official determination is still that Nick slipped and fell of the cliff, but the thing is, I went out to the place where he died, and I don't think the authorities have even bothered to look any further than the spot where they found Nick's body.<br><br>\tThere was caution tape down on the rocks, but nothing on top of the cliff.'<br><br>F2:\t<span id=\"node8_169254084843023138\" class=\"highlighted\">What's she saying about</span>, they didn't even\u2026can I see that sentence?<br><br>\t'<span id=\"node13_169254084843023138\" class=\"highlighted\">They didn't bother to look any further than the spot where they found Nick's body</span>.<br><br>\tOkay, so <span id=\"node21_169254084843023138\" class=\"highlighted\">they haven't investigated the area</span>.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br><br>F1:\tSo she's saying, 'Caution tape on the rocks, but nothing up at the top of the cliff, near the ledge.&nbsp; It didn't look like it had been disturbed since Saturday night, and if the authorities had been there, there's no way they'd count out foul play.&nbsp; Someone in a devil mask really was there that night, and whoever it was, pushed Nick off that cliff.<br><br>\tThe sheriff may not believe me, but I must be making someone nervous by looking into Nick's death.&nbsp;<br><br>[00:02:20]: I've started to get threatening letters, just like the ones Nick was getting before he died.&nbsp; I'd be lying if I said I'm not scared, but those threats also prove I'm onto something, don't you think?'<br><br>F2:\tShe should be.&nbsp; I think so.<br><br>F1:\t'I know I'm close, but I've got questions I can't answer.&nbsp; I'm sending you all the evidence I've collected in the hope that you'll be able to do what I can't, and bring my friend's killer to justice before it's too late.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br><br>[00:02:37]: Sincerely, Carmen.<br>",
